In order to build the INDI qhy drivers, you must have:
cmake installed
libusb 1.0.xx (libusb 0.1 is not supported) along with the header files,
INDI installed along with the header files,
cfitsio installed

Run:
cmake .
make
sudo make install

To test the build execute standalone application (requires libusb 1.0 only)

qhy_test
